msgid "Set up sample data and a pre-built workbook to explore Insights features."
msgstr "Nastavte ukážkové dáta a predpripravený zošit, aby ste mohli preskúmať funkcie Insights."

msgid "Set the start of the fiscal year for the organization. This will be used to calculate quarterly and yearly data."
